### 2. Research Before Assuming
When uncertain about implementation details, investigate first.
See [Research Workflow](claude-docs/research-workflow.md).

### 3. Self-Documenting Code
Code should be clear without comments. Use meaningful names.
Comments explain "why", not "what".
See [Code Quality](claude-docs/code-quality.md).

### 4. Document Decisions
Significant architectural decisions go in ADRs.
